value.0: All citizens of the Sharakhan Empire are asked to choose a Crest upon their graduation. The three Crests represent the three paths by which they serve the Emperor: that of the Guardian, that of the Enforcer, and that of the Redeemer.

All citizens of the Sharakhan Empire are asked to choose a Crest upon their graduation. The three Crests represent the three paths by which they serve the Emperor: that of the Guardian, that of the Enforcer, and that of the Redeemer.
Emperor Rakha's stony gaze bears down on you.
